    "client_msg_id": "86b9f6d2-ae36-4433-93dd-692fcb3252b9",
    "text": "I agree, but, I think that this is a problem. Conflating 2 concepts generally makes the solution 10x harder. We must use assembler to program CPUs, but, we don't actually need to be using sequential coding languages for anything higher level than that.",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1737943315.554909",
    "parent_user_id": "UCUSW7WVD",
    "blocks": [
      {
